{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/111589", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/111589/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/111589/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/111589/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/111589", "id": 1709804308, "node_id": "I_kwDOAAsO6M5l6YsU", "number": 111589, "title": "attribute macros have no access to attributes defined before them", "user": {"login": "roignpar", "id": 47150492, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQ3MTUwNDky", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/47150492?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/roignpar", "html_url": "https://github.com/roignpar", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/roignpar/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/roignpar/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/roignpar/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/roignpar/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/roignpar/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/roignpar/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/roignpar/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/roignpar/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/roignpar/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 650731663, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 1, "created_at": "2023-05-15T10:34:15Z", "updated_at": "2023-05-15T13:29:44Z", "closed_at": "2023-05-15T13:29:44Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "While debugging https://github.com/roignpar/optfield/issues/4 I noticed that attribute macros only have access to attributes defined after them. As all the [documentation](https://doc.rust-lang.org/reference/procedural-macros.html#attribute-macros) I could find on the subject states that \"The second TokenStream is the rest of the item including **other** attributes on the item\", I thought this could be a bug since order of attributes is never mentioned.\r\nIt might as well just be missing documentation(?).\r\n\r\nI tried this code:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\n#[before]\r\n#[after]\r\nstruct Item;\r\n```\r\n\r\nI expected to see this happen: if `after` is an attribute macro it would receive `#[before]` as part of it's item `TokenStream`.\r\n\r\nInstead, this happened: it doesn't.\r\n\r\nI initially thought this had something to do with `syn`: https://github.com/dtolnay/syn/issues/1452\r\n\r\n### Meta\r\n<!--\r\nIf you're using the stable version of the compiler, you should also check if the\r\nbug also exists in the beta or nightly versions.\r\n-->\r\n\r\n`rustc --version --verbose`:\r\n```\r\nrustc 1.69.0 (84c898d65 2023-04-16)\r\nbinary: rustc\r\ncommit-hash: 84c898d65adf2f39a5a98507f1fe0ce10a2b8dbc\r\ncommit-date: 2023-04-16\r\nhost: x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu\r\nrelease: 1.69.0\r\nLLVM version: 15.0.7\r\n```\r\n\r\n", "closed_by": {"login": "ehuss", "id": 43198, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQzMTk4", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/43198?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/ehuss", "html_url": "https://github.com/ehuss", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ehuss/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ehuss/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ehuss/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ehuss/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ehuss/subsc